[div class=p 
	[em 
		"SINCLAIR 01: The Trail Begins
	]em
	" is a biographical text adventure game for the ZX Spectrum. It was developed as a tribute to Sir Clive Sinclair, the founder of the company that created the ZX Spectrum, Sinclair Research. It is based on the early years of Sinclair himself, specifically around the time when he was 18 years old. Follow and guide him through those times as he decides what to do with his life and whether or not he'll go into a career in electronics.
